{"tid":1831112,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老味下星期一年初三重播智叔廖啟智演藝生涯最經典作品","createTime":"2020-01-20T07:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T08:08:39.000Z","uid":92376,"like":21,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e961287c379568c96606fcba0adf1123f40edc2c","tid":1831112,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:04:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大冬瓜</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n02:45PM<br />\n大冬瓜#1[粵]  <br />\n<br />\n統吃的冬瓜盅竟是皇母娘娘賀壽之物，娘關他在大冬瓜內五百年靜思己過。五百年後，貴兄長富只懂賭博及借錢，其妻凌鳳跟人私奔。富得罪了狐妖霍思思，她施法令富連家傳的雜貨店也輸掉。玉與貴被困山洞，發現了大冬瓜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366f7191ff6f83db3f25a79d264c67f044f339c6","tid":1831112,"uid":224375,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:05:20.000Z","msg":"大冬瓜，鳩毛開叉"},{"pid":"1f5efb37ad754c5b04c1f31e74c31e73e009558e","tid":1831112,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"366f7191ff6f83db3f25a79d264c67f044f339c6","tid":1831112,"uid":224375,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:05:20.000Z","msg":"大冬瓜，鳩毛開叉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d9691bf3c863305a547c4a8611b75fedc2f0c5","tid":1831112,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:31:26.000Z","msg":"2009年03月10日<br />\n继《十兄弟》、《搜神传》后，无线再度炮制神怪科幻剧，当初被指是仓底货的《十兄弟》突然创下收视佳绩，证明这类剧种有一定捧场客。该剧监制潘嘉德就表示《大冬瓜》老少咸宜，希望观众看得开心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，他还透露：&ldquo;《大冬瓜》选用了《十兄弟》班底，吸收了上次拍摄教训，特技也比《十兄弟》更好。我们不想让人觉得老气，所以服饰上参考了《清明上河图》，画面上有缤纷的感觉。&rdquo;这也是2004年离开无线后，廖启智首度回巢拍剧，潘嘉德也说他是男主角&ldquo;范统&rdquo;的不二人选。"},{"pid":"84be9d8e5e28f546d856a58162e7fcb2fbeba9f7","tid":1831112,"uid":7439,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:31:59.000Z","msg":"香港連續劇09喜劇大冬瓜 廖啟智 陳錦鴻 胡定欣雙碟DVD<br />\n<br />\n已售出<br />\n$168<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3c2902ca855d3d5dd54bf9e03a86dbe3df7874","tid":1831112,"uid":7439,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:34:12.000Z","msg":"有網民提出希望智叔拍《大冬瓜2》，智叔聽後則露出驚喜的表情說：「是嗎？都幾開心的，那是給小朋友放學後有一個輕鬆的時間看的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其實拍那套戲的時候我都好開心。」"},{"pid":"360d039bc6ee8db35da10acc0532e3b19df58a83","tid":1831112,"uid":242224,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當年食飯<br />\n睇其中一段   唔覺意笑左<br />\n當下覺得自己好唔爭氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aad0be32fce7dbb6ea22e3e1102ff30681a6885","tid":1831112,"uid":53705,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"4d3c2902ca855d3d5dd54bf9e03a86dbe3df7874","tid":1831112,"uid":7439,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:34:12.000Z","msg":